<plot>This is a Bolshoi Ballet version of Anna Karenina. Anna (Plisetskaya) and a younger Vronsky (Godunov) are expressing their love through dance. Anna is torn between her love for the handsome Count Vronky and her loveless marriage to an older husband. Entourage is provided by the Bolshoi Theater Ballet and Simphony Orchestra.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?041391</url></doc>
